@startuml Sequence_Candidate_Authentication
title Ứng Viên - Đăng Ký & Đăng Nhập (Module A)

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng viên"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant AuthService as "Auth\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Đăng Ký Ứng Viên ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Mở form đăng ký
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show registration form
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Nhập email, password, fullName
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Validate input
FrontEnd -> AuthService: POST /api/auth/dang-ky-ung-vien\n(email, password, fullName)
AuthService -> AuthService: Hash password
AuthService -> Database: Check email exists
Database --> AuthService: Email available
AuthService -> Database: Create tai_khoan (CANDIDATE role)\nCreate ung_vien
Database --> AuthService: Return taiKhoanId
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Return JWT token & taiKhoanId
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Đăng ký thành công

== Đăng Nhập ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Đăng nhập"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show login form
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Enter email, password
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Validate input
FrontEnd -> AuthService: POST /api/auth/dang-nhap\n(email, password)
AuthService -> Database: GET tai_khoan (email)
Database --> AuthService: Return tai_khoan
AuthService -> AuthService: Verify password hash
AuthService -> Database: Update last_login
Database --> AuthService: OK
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Return JWT token\n(access & refresh)
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Store JWT locally
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Logged in

== Đăng Xuất ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Đăng xuất"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Clear JWT from storage
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Redirect to login page
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Logged out

== Làm Mới Token ==

FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: JWT expires
FrontEnd -> AuthService: POST /api/auth/lam-moi-token\n(refreshToken)
AuthService -> Database: Validate refresh token
Database --> AuthService: Token valid
AuthService --> FrontEnd: Return new JWT
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Update JWT
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Token refreshed

@enduml
